rlMmwlErrorStatus_t Struct Reference

This is an error status report internally generated from mmWaveLink when it finds any issue with the recieved message or communication. Currently errorVal can be RL_RET_CODE_CRC_FAILED, RL_RET_CODE_CHKSUM_FAILED or RL_RET_CODE_HOSTIRQ_TIMEOUT. Event: RL_MMWL_AE_MISMATCH_REPORT, RL_MMWL_AE_INTERNALERR_REPORT ErroVal: RL_RET_CODE_CRC_FAILED, RL_RET_CODE_CHKSUM_FAILED or RL_RET_CODE_HOSTIRQ_TIMEOUT for RL_MMWL_AE_MISMATCH_REPORT Event and RL_RET_CODE_RADAR_OSIF_ERROR for RL_MMWL_AE_INTERNALERR_REPORT Event. #include <control/mmwavelink/mmwavelink.h>

Detailed Description

This is an error status report internally generated from mmWaveLink when it finds any issue with the recieved message or communication. Currently errorVal can be RL_RET_CODE_CRC_FAILED, RL_RET_CODE_CHKSUM_FAILED or RL_RET_CODE_HOSTIRQ_TIMEOUT. Event: RL_MMWL_AE_MISMATCH_REPORT, RL_MMWL_AE_INTERNALERR_REPORT ErroVal: RL_RET_CODE_CRC_FAILED, RL_RET_CODE_CHKSUM_FAILED or RL_RET_CODE_HOSTIRQ_TIMEOUT for RL_MMWL_AE_MISMATCH_REPORT Event and RL_RET_CODE_RADAR_OSIF_ERROR for RL_MMWL_AE_INTERNALERR_REPORT Event.
